{"tid":1755914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全新[社區戰線]：支援手足、深耕細作、染黃社區、備戰立選","createTime":"2019-11-25T22:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T15:37:11.000Z","uid":267881,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"96debffe1fc15d9e416dbf60cf88bd617891c093","tid":1755914,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T22:38:00.000Z","msg":"中科:別對結果過份樂觀, 其實北京無輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753507</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敵人一個星期遭受幾個重大打擊，短期內一定會亂左陣腳，會驚/質疑/反醒，但佢地最終目標只有一個：調整戰略再反咬你一口。<br />\n如果我地一跟住敵人一齊放慢腳步，其實係冇賺過，所以要盡快收拾心情，以滿血姿態繼續上路，搵出之前密不透風嘅缺口大力打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請全體泛民區議員承諾在體制內與手足同行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n新任區議員你哋聽住，你哋第一件事要做嘅事，就係蛇齋餅糉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753059</a><br />\n<br />\n請所有黃營區議員聯署聲明五大訴求，事前已經講左係變相公投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753826</a><br />\n<br />\n區選會應該趁勢將連儂牆合法化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754083</a><br />\n<br />\n陳偉業: 新議員應翻查「區議會」昔日數簿, 很可能有貪污罪證<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754197</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">體制外嘅冷氣手足都要配合社區戰線，即刻做：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中國人！反抗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1751991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1751991</a><br />\n<br />\n而家最重要係馬上向國際宣佈中共大規模選舉舞弊 唔撚好再係到打飛機!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1752292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1752292</a><br />\n<br />\n「國際戰線」呢個係成場運動以來第一次有數據既民意反映，我地一定要好好對外宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1752544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1752544</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個勢頭 黃色經濟圈一定要馬上加強實行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753833</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">街頭抗爭、黃色經濟圈<br />\n社區戰線、國際戰線、老豆搵仔<br />\n缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\nP牌仔懇求出盡力推上熱門"},{"pid":"18bbebd55a34d39546e103a6f5ad16e536dd72fb","tid":1755914,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T22:55:31.000Z","msg":"放錯台係我岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推上熱門：新戰線&mdash;用建制方法贏建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a172fa3eaa5bfbddc5805dc64aaddce438a00372","tid":1755914,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"呢啲post要推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長期作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501647101414392e183e182c72d8cf1cf1b3d3e3","tid":1755914,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"染黃社區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22663a0a203da5b6a3e96c77359b101a7ed9216a","tid":1755914,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as